{"TopicId":147156,"ForumId":148,"TopicTitle":"Update 1.2 has entered Experimental testing!","CreatedByName":"UomoCapra","CreatedById":167737,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-06T01:44:01Z","PageNum":5,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Eldrad_Ulthran","CreatedById":185228,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-10T00:49:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222748953\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473461695\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258056\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Temeter\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Temeter said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShould affect hardly anything on Kerbin, you just need a tiny antenna on your drone and everything is fine. Or just disable it via options.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank goodness! I just hate to see jeb crash in the kestrel (my WIP)\u00A0thanks to an unexpected spin!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Temeter","CreatedById":58056,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-10T01:34:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222749064\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473468596\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166698\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022owenmaley\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, owenmaley said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank goodness! I just hate to see jeb crash in the kestrel (my WIP)\u00A0thanks to an unexpected spin!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShouldn\u0027t even need a signal if you got jeb on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Eldrad_Ulthran","CreatedById":185228,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-10T05:43:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222749116\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473471261\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258056\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Temeter\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Temeter said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShouldn\u0027t even need a signal if you got jeb on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant that I wanted to not have jeb on it while testing but if not then he might crash.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wolf Baginski","CreatedById":138549,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-10T10:21:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI doubt Porkjet is that careless about mesh structures and texturing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know places where people are that careless, and some people in these parts really need to be more careful about texture sizes for IVAs. It\u0027s quite possible that there are large graphics files as master copies, sitting on Porkjet\u0027s workstation, but we won\u0027t see them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bloojay","CreatedById":162865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T00:14:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy do you guys never include patchnotes??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Temeter","CreatedById":58056,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T00:34:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222750362\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473552840\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bloojay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, Bloojay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy do you guys never include patchnotes??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy do you think they ever not included patchnotes? Oo\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Planetace","CreatedById":195406,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T10:37:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222743622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473126241\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167737\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022UomoCapra\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/6/2016 at 2:44 AM, UomoCapra said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb style=\u0022font-weight:normal;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003EDuring experimental testing a crack team of experienced and hand-picked KSP players will throw everything they\u2019ve got at the game to make it bend, blend and break in many ways. The goal is to catch as many bugs as we can, and to make the game as stable as it can be before we make a public test build available. \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou haven\u0027t heard of Danny2426, have you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Polnoch","CreatedById":153066,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T19:12:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnybody know which features planning in next version, 1.3 (or may be 2.0?)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are no information in official wiki:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Planned_features\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Planned_features\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frybert","CreatedById":97766,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T19:39:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222751260\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473621124\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022153066\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Polnoch\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, Polnoch said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnybody know which features planning in next version, 1.3 (or may be 2.0?)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are no information in official wiki:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Planned_features\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Planned_features\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI \u00A0don\u0027t believe they\u0027ve stated what features are planned for a next version yet. I would recommend waiting until they have finished this version first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T21:00:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222750722\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473590264\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155981\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Galacticvoyager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Galacticvoyager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou haven\u0027t heard of Danny2426, have you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDanny breaks the game in unrealistic ways.\u00A0 With a game this complex sometimes the solution to an odd behavior is to stop doing whatever causes that odd behavior.\u00A0 The testing is not intended to find those kinds of bugs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jeb-head-mug kerman","CreatedById":159289,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T22:11:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinaly!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheGuyNamedAlan","CreatedById":162058,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T22:22:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhoo!!! wheels will be fixed soon!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222750722\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473590264\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155981\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Galacticvoyager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Galacticvoyager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou haven\u0027t heard of Danny2426, have you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor nexter\u0027s lab\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Polnoch","CreatedById":153066,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T22:54:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222751309\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473622782\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002297766\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Frybert\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Frybert said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI \u00A0don\u0027t believe they\u0027ve stated what features are planned for a next version yet. I would recommend waiting until they have finished this version first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut actual features\u00A0included in wiki\u00A0during long time. And in wiki included information\u00A0in which\u00A0versions of games these \u00A0planned\u00A0to integrate. And may be 1.5 years before we knew, for example, about relay network in future versions of\u00A0stock game. Actually no new information about next features. And it is sad, because in the past we had this info.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy curiosity fills small pain \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-11T22:57:30Z\u0022 title=\u002209/11/2016 10:57  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 11, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Polnoch\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T23:01:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222751606\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473634450\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022153066\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Polnoch\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Polnoch said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut actual features\u00A0included in wiki\u00A0during long time. And in wiki included information\u00A0in which\u00A0versions of games these\u00A0planning to integrate. And may be 1.5 years before we knew, for example, about relay network in future versions of\u00A0stock game. Actually no new information about next features. And it is sad, because in the past we had this info.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy curiosity fills small pain \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo note that this information was found and uploaded by the community, not SQUAD. Complaining to SQUAD about the opacity (or nonexistence) of future plans is more appropriate, though still looked down upon.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TedwinKnockman66","CreatedById":155882,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T05:07:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t wait it!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand i Hope you would add a command pod size\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(249,249,249);float:none;\u0022\u003E1.25 with 2 crew members like this:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/o6QatiN.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022o6QatiN.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MatBailie","CreatedById":149545,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T09:37:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222751992\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473656875\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155882\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TedwinKnockman66\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, TedwinKnockman66 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t wait it!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand i Hope you would add a command pod size\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(249,249,249);float:none;\u0022\u003E1.25 with 2 crew members like this:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeck, let\u0027s just add a half-kerbal sized 0.625m command pod too \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkHawkGames","CreatedById":163651,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T12:26:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need this in my life, as soon as possible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Giskard","CreatedById":165799,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T20:23:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222751428\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473627622\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110959\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alshain\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, Alshain said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDanny breaks the game in unrealistic ways.\u00A0 With a game this complex sometimes the solution to an odd behavior is to stop doing whatever causes that odd behavior.\u00A0 The testing is not intended to find those kinds of bugs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, in the company that I am working for, this is something that you have to expect from our customers: They do the most stupid things with our soft- and hardware that no one was ever thinking of. I could tell them they are using it wrong, but often it actually turns out that this helps to fix strange rare and unreproduceable bugs that other customers experience as well. As long as they can tell us what they actually did, of course. But I guess this is something that we can expect from Danny2426...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd after all: I cant tell a paying customer that the solution to his problem to stop doing what he does without presenting him an alternative.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T21:28:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222752797\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473711837\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165799\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Giskard\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Giskard said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, in the company that I am working for, this is something that you have to expect from our customers: They do the most stupid things with our soft- and hardware that no one was ever thinking of. I could tell them they are using it wrong, but often it actually turns out that this helps to fix strange rare and unreproduceable bugs that other customers experience as well. As long as they can tell us what they actually did, of course. But I guess this is something that we can expect from Danny2426...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd after all: I cant tell a paying customer that the solution to his problem to stop doing what he does without presenting him an alternative.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame here, but this a game.\u00A0 If my companies software breaks, my customers lose money.\u00A0 However, in this case it is perfectly acceptable to say not to do things that are so overly ridiculous no one would do that unless they were intentionally trying to break the game. Have you watched Danny\u0027s videos... he really pushes it to it\u0027s limits in ways nobody would even accidentally do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StormKat","CreatedById":126927,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T21:35:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had a client that would call the help desk, \u0022The database is corrupted again.\u0022\u00A0 It took months to determine that he was laying his right hand on the numeric keypad while typing into a field with his left.\u00A0 I was actually asked how to prevent that from happening.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T21:35:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222752897\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473715691\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110959\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alshain\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Alshain said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame here, but this a game.\u00A0 If my companies software breaks, my customers lose money.\u00A0 However, in this case it is perfectly acceptable to say not to do things that are so overly ridiculous no one would do that unless they were intentionally trying to break the game. Have you watched Danny\u0027s videos... he really pushes it to it\u0027s limits in ways nobody would even accidentally do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you trying to say I\u0027m some kind of deviant for making landing cushions out of helmets?! They work almost as well as landing legs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T21:56:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222752917\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473716135\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you trying to say I\u0027m some kind of deviant for making landing cushions out of helmets?! They work almost as well as landing legs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDeviant is a bit strong.. I prefer \u0027eccentric\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Space Cowboy Bob","CreatedById":161283,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T22:54:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222750362\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473552840\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bloojay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/10/2016 at 7:14 PM, Bloojay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy do you guys never include patchnotes??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh? You must be thinking of another game company because there has never been a patch without patch notes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corw","CreatedById":7116,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-13T06:15:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.1 branch has been removed from Steam beta. Waiting intensifies...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"severedsolo","CreatedById":80345,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-13T06:27:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222752797\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022147156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473711837\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165799\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Giskard\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Giskard said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd after all: I cant tell a paying customer that the solution to his problem to stop doing what he does without presenting him an alternative.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWikipedia defines a bug as \u0022\u003Cspan\u003Ean error, flaw, failure or fault in a computer program or system that causes it to produce an incorrect or unexpected result, or to behave in unintended ways.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EIf you set out to break the game, and the game breaks. That\u0027s not unintended or unexpected beahviour.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-13T06:28:03Z\u0022 title=\u002209/13/2016 06:28  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 13, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by severedsolo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}